data.description: Perfect location with Lafayette River views, nestled in Norfolks beautiful and historic Colonial Place. Classic home on a large corner lot boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. Filled with original character and charm throughout, you will not be disappointed! Open layout, enclosed sunroom and screened porch, replacement windows, dual zone HVAC, fully updated kitchen w pantry, bamboo flooring. Enjoy both a sunroom and a screened in porch. 1st floor bed (step down) and bathroom with separate entrance. NICE backyard haven, mature landscaping and trees, relaxing koi pond and privacy fence. Walk-in shower 1st & 2nd floors. Location, location! Conveniently located near N Colley, Riverview and Ghent dining and shopping; interstates, downtown, military bases and MUCH more. WDI issued by Bug-Out. Seller would love to close quickly and rent back to 6/17
